<paragraph id="3AF6DECD89D42CE04C1F7241A5B85724" pageId="null" pageNumber="615">Feuer-Bohne</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
</title>
<subSubSection id="7DB1F61D687F3A553FA5D6367D58C8D5" pageId="null" pageNumber="615" type="description">
<paragraph id="9C6299E8DA49DFD7EC7075AA297C237C" pageId="null" pageNumber="615">
1-bis 
<normalizedToken id="07E3FC48288C4FDE516380979D2A032E" originalValue="mehrjährig" pageId="null" pageNumber="615">mehrjaehrig</normalizedToken>
, windend; 300-400 cm hoch. Stengel, 
<normalizedToken id="10781B0E0FA97CDEE09D10ABEABC9584" originalValue="Blätter" pageId="null" pageNumber="615">Blaetter</normalizedToken>
, 
<normalizedToken id="F4811C2EB142C74CF7954E3E88A87F3C" originalValue="Blütenstiele" pageId="null" pageNumber="615">Bluetenstiele</normalizedToken>
, 
<normalizedToken id="0EDA76AB8D6AE103EC574F2308D0714D" originalValue="Früchte" pageId="null" pageNumber="615">Fruechte</normalizedToken>
und Kelch sehr kurz behaart bis fast kahl. 
<normalizedToken id="D9AA90484058CA3AC52B3BC9E1CD22BF" originalValue="Teilblätter" pageId="null" pageNumber="615">Teilblaetter</normalizedToken>
wie bei 
<taxonomicName id="A56562B5FFC660854F2F9587BABCFCDF" class="Bivalvia" family="Phaseolidae" genus="Phaseolus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Nuculanida" pageId="null" pageNumber="615" phylum="Mollusca" rank="species" species="vulgaris">
<emphasis id="3751AD0B7808D4898FB34EF7636F2793" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="615">Ph. vulgaris</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(Nr. 1). 
<emphasis id="FDDC30C7B67C7F5E7B5BC5BF441ECBF2" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="615">
<normalizedToken id="2C7D7B9643F5FCCC7558933598EF5364" originalValue="Blütenstand" pageId="null" pageNumber="615">Bluetenstand</normalizedToken>
so lang oder 
<normalizedToken id="DC04C9A56F2323D3583A97A83EEE21E2" originalValue="länger" pageId="null" pageNumber="615">laenger</normalizedToken>
als die 
<normalizedToken id="3F819E460C2F733AB1269A56314DCA29" originalValue="Stengelblätter" pageId="null" pageNumber="615">Stengelblaetter</normalizedToken>
. Krone rot oder 
<normalizedToken id="1933CB1E9C0FCC086586563D171202ED" originalValue="weiß" pageId="null" pageNumber="615">weiss</normalizedToken>
, 1,5-3 cm lang.
</emphasis>
Frucht 12-20 cm lang, 3-5samig. 
<emphasis id="DE22C02CE33DE026326DD2686A7CB463" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="615">Samen 13-25 mm lang.</emphasis>
- 
<normalizedToken id="6252295874D48F965440725AD4C84DB3" originalValue="Blüte" pageId="null" pageNumber="615">Bluete</normalizedToken>
: Sommer.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="7AB610699C4C8AF32C7041B25220321F" pageId="null" pageNumber="615">
<emphasis id="BD54F47C5D4EF628EA4A9C3392E375FC" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="615">Zytologische Angaben. 2n</emphasis>
= 
<emphasis id="6B368A6DF65E7297132F79D1D88C53BE" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="615">22:</emphasis>
Material aus Kulturen (verschiedene Autoren bei 
<normalizedToken id="9B2423C6704AEC1B45B4545F3DDCB9C0" originalValue="Löve" pageId="null" pageNumber="615">Loeve</normalizedToken>
und 
<normalizedToken id="EF420C1A49A3C09BBA7AD301F321117E" originalValue="Löve" pageId="null" pageNumber="615">Loeve</normalizedToken>
1961, 
<normalizedToken id="7B0286F93ABA5E20D4C8259178B3E971" originalValue="Maréchal" pageId="null" pageNumber="615">Marechal</normalizedToken>
1969).
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="021A7ACA63D23F9E8C2C40804AFC7AC7" pageId="null" pageNumber="615">
<emphasis id="64583F3EF48644E397BAF7F3C4AF1C92" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="615">Standort.</emphasis>
Wie 
<taxonomicName id="DD8F783B80A3BE610A9E4F1E34FA9643" class="Bivalvia" family="Phaseolidae" genus="Phaseolus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Nuculanida" pageId="null" pageNumber="615" phylum="Mollusca" rank="species" species="vulgaris">
<emphasis id="BBFF605AC3E529BB811C2F2148E3EB82" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="615">Ph. vulgaris</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(Nr. 1), aber etwas weniger 
<normalizedToken id="52DF685F8B598857144A1EE9F00CABAE" originalValue="kälteempfindlich" pageId="null" pageNumber="615">kaelteempfindlich</normalizedToken>
.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="39FC9B52D8586D5509F883D0D695079F" pageId="null" pageNumber="615">
<emphasis id="5E8DC90D165E5CAF9DAC690766E4F077" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="615">
Verbreitung. Mittel- und 
<normalizedToken id="04AF13726A2CD9664EA8CA0C07704A9B" originalValue="südamerikanische" pageId="null" pageNumber="615">suedamerikanische</normalizedToken>
Pflanze.
</emphasis>
- Im Gebiet als Zierpflanze oder 
<normalizedToken id="9C2B1C9AB5F68CF2D64BE2A6F1F3D019" originalValue="Gemüse" pageId="null" pageNumber="615">Gemuese</normalizedToken>
kultiviert.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
